sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant U as Assinante
    participant App as App Casa Conectada
    participant PING as PING / CIAM
    participant APG as Apigee
    participant BFF as BFF Claro

    U->>App: Credentials / OAuth2 flow
    App->>PING: OAuth2 authorization
    PING-->>App: Session tokens (ex.: access / id)
    App->>APG: API HTTPS + token (gateway policies)
    APG->>BFF: Pedido validado / roteado
    Note over BFF: Business identity: CPF<br/>and contract context
